window.bookSummaryJSON = "Buried deep in the past of a quiet southern town lies the legend of Billy Sunday Birt, the most dangerous man in Georgia history. A chance meeting one spring day unravels the truth behind the notorious figure and uncovers new secrets along the way. \"A wild tale of moonshine, murder, and mayhem\" - Vulture 2021 Webby Award Honoree, Podcast Limited Series"; 
